    "causal_summary": "Phase 015/003 shipped the lane-weight sweep harness, the type extension, and a 24-prompt corpus, but the sweep run produced byte-identical numbers across all 7 candidate vectors (including V6-cosine-dominant at semantic=0.30). Root cause documented in 015/003 implementation-summary.md Known Limitation #2: the sweep test runs against `createFixtureProjection(...)` which does NOT seed the `embedding` column that the cosine lane reads via `loadSkillEmbeddings()`. So semantic_shadow contributed zero to every vector regardless of weight, and the sweep is currently a regression guard on the four non-semantic lanes only.",
